# Transient atheris/libfuzzer artifacts — keep human-curated seeds + crash
# artifacts under version control, drop the rest.

# Per-run summary logs written by the harnesses (`> last_*.log`).
last_run.log
last_cose_sig_run.log
last_cose_bundle_run.log

# Coverage-extending entries libfuzzer adds during a run, named by SHA-1 of
# their contents (40-char hex). The named `seed_*` files in each corpus
# subdir are the curated baseline and ARE committed; everything else is
# regeneratable noise.
corpus/manifest/[0-9a-f][0-9a-f]*
corpus/cose/[0-9a-f][0-9a-f]*
corpus/cose_bundle/[0-9a-f][0-9a-f]*
